  "title": "Relief Teacher (Pre-School)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Assistance in establishing an effective and responsive classroom environment where children are active participants</li><li>Contributing to maintaining a positive learning environment</li><li>Observe children in play in order to assist in the planning, implementation and evaluation of the child centred curriculum for both the indoor and outdoor learning environments</li><li>Assist in supporting the positive development of children’s social competencies</li><li>Assist in the routine care of children (meal, toileting, rest)</li><li>Maintenance of materials, resources and equipments in classrooms</li><li>Assist in the professional documentation and display of children’s work</li><li>Support and maintain positive classroom relationships where all members of the class are respected and valued</li><li>Assist and support all preschool functions</li><li>Participate in any preschool events as assigned.</li></ul>",
